# Architecture

## Architecture Style

Layered Architecture

```text
API Layer
    ↓
Application Layer
    ↓
Domain Layer
    ↓
Infrastructure Layer
```

---

## Components

### API

Responsibilities:

- Request validation
- Response serialization
- HTTP error handling

Technology:

- FastAPI
- Pydantic

---

### Application Layer

Responsibilities:

- Use cases
- Transaction boundaries
- Search orchestration
- Source management

Services:

- SearchService
- SourceService
- IngestionService

---

### Domain Layer

Contains:

- Entities
- Repository contracts
- Business rules

No framework dependencies allowed.

---

### Infrastructure Layer

Contains:

- PostgreSQL access
- pgvector integration
- Feed parsers
- HTML extraction
- Embedding generation
- Scheduler

---

## Background Processing

Scheduler:

- APScheduler

Jobs:

- Feed synchronization
- Article ingestion
- Embedding generation

Default interval:

- Every 15 minutes

---

## Data Flow

```text
Configured Source
        ↓
feedparser
        ↓
Article URL
        ↓
BeautifulSoup
        ↓
Text Extraction
        ↓
Chunking
        ↓
SentenceTransformer
        ↓
Embedding
        ↓
PostgreSQL + pgvector
```

---

## Search Flow

```text
Query
  ↓
Embedding
  ↓
pgvector similarity search
  ↓
Top Results
```